{"type": "article", "id": 63297, "title": "优酷换了新 Logo，肯德基母亲节广告有争议 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-04-26T04:57:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 418, "name": "母亲节"}, {"id": 18657, "name": "食物浪费"}, {"id": 1700, "name": "优酷"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 28, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190426122109uXKLqk8JxRtI6EPT.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"33VP\">GAP 成立 50 周年之际，<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1833496740/4364873590626043\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宣布蔡依林成为大中华区代言人。</b></a>她和 Gap 50 位个性共同推广”我是______，我值得被庆祝“话题活动，Gap 传递释放个性，每个人值得被肯定。此外，Gap 还推出了限定版音乐概念 Music T。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122147k2joPID1fMbWV0Ay.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.733333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122147CSrEF5xXJGf8AHsB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.733333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"e7RO\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1642904381/4364911347333255\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>优酷换了新 Logo。</b></a> 配色由原来的红蓝配色，变成了粉红粉蓝。Logo 去掉小圆点设计，更加扁平化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122207rz8CyVeMmtPnXf9E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.792233\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"diTy\"><b><a href=\"https://www.campaignlive.com/article/coca-cola-basically-controls-mind-new-campaign/1583039\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">可口可乐发布了一组 </a><a href=\"https://www.campaignlive.com/article/coca-cola-basically-controls-mind-new-campaign/1583039\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Synesthesia 平面广告。</a></b>Synesthesia 即中文中的通感。人们看到这组广告时，耳边不自觉响起：瓶盖打开的一声”嘭“，拉环开启的响动甚至是可乐倒入杯中、气泡呲呲跳跃的声音。创意代理商是 David。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122220lKfyVaLButmP4EXR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904261222215TQFBDW72RgizVrs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122221RqXA9S0LeVHMvo3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"H3px\"><a href=\"https://st.music.163.com/c/drawing/QEv9bNc4Dw/index.html?userid=16514227\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>网易云音乐和 M2 创意工作室共同推出”心理绘画“活动。</b></a>用户根据给定的图形绘画并用一个词语形容。网易云音乐称据心理学家 Ehrig Wartegg 的理论，这项测试能挖掘内心潜意识。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122524JaukByIZQxgsSGov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.713333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122622Co5h3wtrbQHYOvTJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.708000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"hIN0\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODY0NDk0MQ==&amp;mid=2656030907&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=266f3d9839162ed2931cdc3a3241ed69&amp;chksm=bd7ced198a0b640f959545acf37fc078564a1f1ed125858c765175bed1894d31c66a919259f6&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=&amp;key=f1b1b4aaf75e0cb58964490f6b92a9d23fe8fddc013718dfd3981bcaae36442f4d222cdab2b191d25ed1138d91ef89c7f571aab63fd561b81e56f2ac8077f7ce7c9485331a1e3b693a2ec449b0428ab7&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=DhManajDsCr4viTrhxggLcuKcG58tVQcZZjt%2FTCeGSWdtXRTU4Ol4ynWUNBCsjBw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>民生信用卡开了一家“深夜银行”。</b></a>深夜故事是主打部分，参与者可以聆听内设的不同主题故事，生成“深夜气质”，6 个深夜故事把握用户心理还是挺准确的。创意代理商是环时互动。其他互动操作例如积分兑换礼物，并没太多新意。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122453xI4vf2JPK8GHoMmb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.720000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122453TYHGomc7y8SwBL3i.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.930667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"lslE\"><a href=\"https://chickendales.com/film/bf3ccd7a-90b6-4d04-abca-8b24cfbce81e\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>肯德基母亲节广告上演猛男秀。</b></a>肯德基上校从爷爷变成了年轻网红，片中上校带着一群年轻男性展示身材和肌肉。视频发布之后，引起不小的讨论，YouTube 的第一条评论是”这太不舒服了“。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s0864t996qc\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"8D0t\"><a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/ikea-new-logo-seventy-agency-04-25-2019/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宜家推出一个新 Logo。</b></a>不过变化很细微。新 Logo 变得更加方正，色彩饱和度降低。此外，新 Logo 字体取消了边角折线。这是宜家 27 年来首次改动 Logo，它由斯德哥尔摩创意机构 Seventy Agency 设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904261227514xa5dQOMrbyNzGUL.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.413793\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122751tMJ0TBzYVoj9Zvh1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.536667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"uboD\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTEyNjQ3MA==&amp;mid=2649692460&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=38f17e6e5be7647331ca15f3cf21a24b&amp;chksm=bea1ff8589d676932d43e90f32a38738c281f30657c14e18dd85a09789ca4e164e23c3472308&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1&amp;key=e26fe09897582c586dc4d2418216e0900ada13b51a657e7d53b246e97499c3ef78e2406b264fe592e5207f62aba3c65c9f8bd962d7b501b85096979c37e6fbcdb42486b75732fadcd08fa59956170de6&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=DhManajDsCr4viTrhxggLcuKcG58tVQcZZjt%2FTCeGSWdtXRTU4Ol4ynWUNBCsjBw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google 在停止食物浪费日（4 月 24 日至 4 月 26 日）期间，展示了管理食材的方法，</b></a>分享日常食物保存方法，避免食物浪费，延长食用期限。 Google 用自己食堂的创意菜“萝卜至上”冰淇淋举例，把一根萝卜完整利用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190426122855XOdHQxmpkSe06gwB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.157576\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"a4Ap\"><a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2019/04/25/snap-hires-first-cmo-kenny-mitchell.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Snapchat 任命首位 CMO Kenny Mitchell。</b></a>他之前是麦当劳美国市场品牌内容与参与副总裁。在这之前，他是佳得乐的消费参与主管，他曾策划营销活动鼓励消费者使用 Snapchat 视频和 AR 工具。</p><p line=\"IAqw\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/UA1cwhy2DRY?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">An Tran</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/fried-chicken?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}